# Install

1. Copy `CLAUDE.md` to the repo root.
2. Copy the entire `.claude/` folder into the repo root.
3. Review `.claude/settings.json` and tighten or loosen permissions for your machine.
4. Open Claude Code in the repo and confirm slash commands load.
5. Run `/repo-audit`, then `/trust-hardening`, then `/website-deep-audit https://djai.vercel.app`.

## What this package includes
- 1 root `CLAUDE.md`
- 10 commands
- 8 agents
- 8 skills
- 5 checklists
- 1 roadmap alignment note
- 1 audit report

